OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773436319
OL,3,CGuernsey's mail plane axed due to costs
OL,5,FGuernsey Post will withdraw its
OL,6,Fdedicated mail plane service to the UK
OL,7,Fblaming rising costs, and instead all
OL,8,Fpost will be transported by sea.
OL,10,FThe final outbound flight will be
OL,11,FFriday July 3rd..
OL,13,FThe company says the rising supply
OL,14,Fchain costs mean it is no longer cost
OL,15,Feffective to operate a dedicated
OL,16,Faircraft each weekday, and moving the
OL,17,Fstandard mail to sea is a "practical
OL,18,Fand commercially" responsible way to
OL,19,Fmaintain a reliable service for all
OL,20,Fcustomers.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
