FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773436319
OL,3,CGuernsey's mail plane axed due to costs
OL,5,FIn a statement it says they are
OL,6,Ftalking to other aircraft carriers to
OL,7,Ftry and maintain a next day service
OL,8,Ffor urgent items.
OL,10,FIt comes less than a year after
OL,11,FGuernsey Post decided only outbound
OL,12,Fpost would travel by air, after Royal
OL,13,FMail decided to withdraw funding for
OL,14,Fthe plane.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
