OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773436319
OL,3,CGuernsey's mail plane axed due to costs
OL,5,FChief Executive Steve Sheridan said:
OL,6,F"Our priority is to provide a
OL,7,Freliable, well-managed and financially
OL,8,Fsustainable postal service for the
OL,9,Fisland. Transitioning standard mail to
OL,10,Fsea allows for that whilst also
OL,11,Fprotecting essential services for
OL,12,Fthose who depend on them."
OL,14,FHe added that customers should not see
OL,15,Fany impact.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@ZO]
