OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773436319
OL,3,CGuernsey's mail plane axed due to costs
OL,5,F"If they are looking for next day
OL,6,Fguarantee services they are still
OL,7,Favailable, and of course remember, we
OL,8,Fhave a very resilient boat service
OL,9,Falready and all of the mail and
OL,10,Fparcels that arrive in the island come
OL,11,Fin by boat, we're expecting to see
OL,12,Fvery little disruption for the
OL,13,Fconsumer."
OL,15,FCustomers have been advised to now
OL,16,Fallow an additional 24 hours for their
OL,17,Fitems to connect with UK deliveries.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
