PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773436319
OL,3,CGuernsey's mail plane axed due to costs
OL,5,FThe card companies based in Guernsey
OL,6,Fwho rely on next day delivery, have
OL,7,Fboth said they plan to remain in the
OL,8,Fisland despite the change.
OL,10,FFunky Pigeon said in a statement: "We
OL,11,Fare working closely with Guernsey Post
OL,12,Fon future arrangements and remain
OL,13,Fcommitted to our fulfilment centre in
OL,14,FGuernsey, which plays a key role in
OL,15,Fserving our customers."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
