OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773436319
OL,3,CGuernsey's mail plane axed due to costs
OL,5,FWhilst Moonpig said: "We are aware of
OL,6,FGuernsey Post's confirmed plans to
OL,7,Fwithdraw the dedicated weekday plane
OL,8,Fto the UK, but Moonpig intends to
OL,9,Fcontinue operating from our site on
OL,10,Fthe island."
OL,12,FStaff at Guernsey Post have also been
OL,13,Ftold that they are reviewing
OL,14,Foperational working hours to align
OL,15,Fwith the revised schedule of the
OL,16,Fboats, and are working with union
OL,17,Frepresentatives to ensure any changes
OL,18,Fare carefully planned and staff
OL,19,Fsupported.
