PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773436319
OL,3,CGuernsey's mail plane axed due to costs
OL,5,FJersey lost its mail plane in August
OL,6,F2023 after Royal Mail decided it would
OL,7,Fno longer fund it because it wasn't
OL,8,Fcommercially viable. Since then all
OL,9,Fpost has been delivered by sea.
